Package: python3-pyperplan
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Lightweight STRIPS planner written in Python. (Python 3)
 Pyperplan supports the following PDDL fragment: STRIPS without action costs.
 .
 Please note that Pyperplan deliberately prefers clean code over fast code.
 It is designed to be used as a teaching or prototyping tool.
 If you use it for paper experiments, please state clearly that Pyperplan
 does not offer state-of-the-art performance.
 .
 This package installs the library for Python 3.
